<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html lang="en">
<%include partials/templates/html_head%>
<body>
<%include partials/templates/header%>

<main>
    <section class="lead">
        <div class="container">
            <article class="lead__content">
                <p class="">Welcome on the Polish Ski Jumpers Fan Page for winter season 2016/2017.
                    This website was made as a web developement project, that main goal was to practice Express Js.
                    Please go to <a href="/about" title="Go to About page" class="content__link">'About'</a> section for more details.
                </p>
                <p class="">What will you find here? Information about 2016/2017 season such as: polish squad with jumpers details,
                    calendar of all events and details of all ski jumping hill that will host competitions.
                </p>
                <p class="">Welcome in the world of this beautiful sport, where all it matters is pure competition and no negative
                    emotions! Enjoy this journey!</p>
            </article>
        </div>

    </section><!--lead-->

    <section class="details">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row-flex">
                <div class="contests">
                    <div class="contests__item">
                        <h2>Last contest</h2>
                        <span><%=prevEvent.date%>, <%=prevEvent.place%><img src="images/<%=prevEvent.country%>.png"></span>
                        <span>Type: <%=prevEvent.type%></span>

                    </div>
                    <div class="contests__item">
                        <h2>Next contest</h2>
                        <span><%=nextEvent.date%>, <%=nextEvent.place%><img src="images/<%=nextEvent.country%>.png"></span>
                        <span>Type: <%=nextEvent.type%></span>
                    </div>


                </div>
                <iframe class="iframe" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vN9HLTqCUXk" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>

<%include partials/templates/footer%>

<%include partials/templates/scripts%>
</body>
</html>
